24... Bc8
{ In the game, I defended too passively with @@StartFEN@@r1b2rk1/2R3p1/pB1pq2p/1p2p3/4Pn2/1P2QN1P/1P3PP1/3R2K1 w - - 5 25@@EndFEN@@  25.Ne1  . What would have been better? }
