[SetUp "1"]

12. b4 { What did I play to muddy the waters? } 12... Nexd5 13. exd5 Nxd5
{ A difficult decision to make, because I am giving away my knight for just two pawns. At the same time, I free up my bishop on b7 while the bishop on g7 also becomes kind of active. I'm threatening to play ...Nd3 followed by ...d5. So this was, of course, a shocking sacrifice for my opponent. }
