[Round "?"]
[White "1) FM to Strong IM"]
[Black "Rasul Ibrahimov vs. Levon Aronian â Puzzle #2"]
[Result "*"]
[FEN "r2q1rk1/pb3pbp/1p1p2p1/2pnp3/1P6/P1PBB2P/3NNPP1/R2Q1RK1 w - - 0 14"]
[SetUp "1"]

14. Nc4 { What should Black play here? } 14... e4
{ The best move. Marching forward in the center. } 15. Bxe4
{ This is a mistake. } 15... Nxe3 16. fxe3 Bxe4
{ The bishop is gone and Black regains his piece with a better position. } *


[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
