19. Qf1 { How to deal with the pressure against f7? } 19... Bd5
{ Quite often we're told that we're supposed to hold on to those two bishops because it is such a powerful combination. And it is a powerful combination, but it is important not to fall in love with your pieces.  At the end of the day, pieces are like colours in a painting. You're going to use the colours you need, but you are not going to paint everything in one colour. And here, if we look at the position, what does White have? One good bishop and nothing else. }
