16... Qc7 { White has now a powerful way to continue the attack. Which one? }
17. f4 { Even stronger than  17.c4  . } 17... b5 18. Qc2 Nc4 19. f5
{ An important intermediate move. } 19... Rf6 20. Bc1
{ 20.Bc5  allows Black to get back in the game with  20...Bf8  21.Bf2  Kg8  , which was eventually won by Black in  Ftacnik-Vaganian, Moscow 1985. }
20... Kg8 21. Ng3 { White's initiative is hard to stop. } *


