12. Bd3 { Find the best continuation for Black. } 12... b6
{ The best move, with the same idea I showed earlier, simply bringing the knight back.   Instead, I committed a very educational mistake by playing  12...Bf8  and the reason why I'm showing this game is because I want to discuss what it means to have illusions. Something we're told from childhood where, when we face it, we understand that this is not that easy or good. }
13. c4 Nb7 { The threat is ...Bf8 when Black is totally fine. } *


[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
