[FEN "4rrk1/ppqnbppp/2b5/2p1p3/P1N1P1P1/1BP2Q1P/1P3P2/R1B1R1K1 w - - 0 17"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ How did I keep increasing the pressure on the kingside? } 17. h4
{ A tricky move! What would happen if Black takes the pawn? } 17... Bxh4 18. g5
{ And the bishop is going to suffer a lot. } *


[Event "?"]
