[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "2) Establishing as a GM"]
[Black "Levon Aronian vs. Arsen Yegiazarian â Puzzle #3"]
[Result "*"]
[FEN "4rr2/ppq2pk1/5np1/P1p1p2p/4P1Pb/1BP2Q2/1P3PK1/R1B1R3 w - - 0 24"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ Arsen missed something here and I hope you won't miss it as well! What is wrong with ...h5? }
