[SetUp "1"]

13. b4
{ What I'm doing has so far been quite normal. I'm trying to at some point play c5 to lock up his b7-bishop. If I manage this, even with a sacrifice, it would make sense if I can stop Black from playing ...c5.What did my opponent play here? }
13... c5
{ My opponent played  13...c5  immediately, which is a very good move. It immediately prevents White from playing c5 at some point. }
*


[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
