20. Nf4
{ @@StartFEN@@3r1rk1/pb2q1pp/np2pb2/8/1PP1p3/6PB/3BPPNP/2R1QRK1 b - - 6 19@@EndFEN@@The point of  19...Be5  is that it's trying to stop Nf4, which was extremely annoying as a threat. If I now play  20.Nf4  ,  what can Black do? }
20... Bxf4 { Black can just take. } 21. Bxf4 Nxb4 { And grab the b4-pawn. } *


[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
