23... Nb8 { What did I play here? } 24. Qd2 Rfe8
{ I found the most elegant move, which I hope you will also find. How does White immediately benefit from the passivity of Black's pieces? }
25. c5
{ I'm now also threatening to play Nc4 and the knight can enter on d6. I'm getting my pawn on the dark squares, and will then try to remove his only good piece, the queen on e5. }
