30. Bb5+
{ Black has a tough mission ahead, but not an impossible one. Try to defend to the best of your abilities! }
30... Kd8
{ After  30...Kf8  ,  the king is too exposed because of the typical maneuver  31.Rh3  . Black's king is getting too much attention. Rg3 and Bh6 are coming. }
31. Rxc5 Qe4
{ I also thought about  31...Qxg2  32.Bg5+  Qxg5  33.Rxg5  Bxh1  34.Bc4  . This position is pleasant for White. I will capture on a5 and then b4 and h5 will be weak. Perhaps it's not a winning advantage but I'm pushing for the win without risking anything. }
32. Ke2
