36... Rf2
{ This is the moment White was looking for: Black succumbed to the tension and the last move is a blunder. Can you tell me why is ...Rf2 a wrong call? }
37. Rg6
{ Black is already lost since the rooks cannot be exchanged and the g7-pawn will fall. }
