37. Qe6
{ Black is walking on a tightrope, but the position is defendable. Find the most accurate way to hold on to a draw. }
37... Qg6 { Black has to bring the queen to deliver the saving checks. } 38.
Qh3+ Kg7 39. Qd7+ Kh6 40. exf6 Bxf6
