31. exf5 { How should Black recapture? } 31... gxf5
{ Svidler thought he had it all covered but miscalculated and took back with the e-pawn. The only way to draw the game was by recapturing with the g-pawn, which looks rather odd as it hands White a passed pawn. }
32. Ne5 Be4
