[SetUp "1"]

2. Ra7
{ White's move seems logical, but, unfortunately, it is not winning. Find the emergency exit for Black. }
2... Re1 3. Kd6
{ 3.Kf6  Rf1+  and now White doesn't have  4.Ke7  since that will obviously lose the rook after  4...Rf7+  . }
